p: In the District Court of the 3d Judisial Distrist of Washington Territory hold at Seattle in and for the counties of King, Kistap and Snohomish.
In the matter of the application of Peter Nelson W Smith H Elsner C Whaly G Matson Charles Lundblad Denns Coffey & Jasob Annir for a writ of Habeas Corpus } Order granting writ

When reading and filing the petition of Peter Nelson W Smith H Elsner C Whaly G Mattson Charles Lundblad Dennis Coffy & Jasob Annir duly signed and verified by them whereas it appears that they are illegally imprisoned and restrained of their liberty by Louis V Wyskoff Sheriff of said County of King in the County jail of King County aforesaid, and stating wherein the alleged illegaliy consists from which it appears to me that a writ of Habeas Corpus ought to issue.

It is ordered that a writ of Habeas Corpus issue out of
and under the seal of the District Court aforesaid, dirested to the said Louis V Wyskoff commanding him to have the bodies of the said Peter Nelso W Smith H Elsen C Whaly G Mattson Charles Lundblad Dennis Coffey & Jasob Annir before me at my chambers in the City of Seattle and County of King aforesaid on the 3 day of May AD 1875 at 1 oClosk PM of that day, to do and resieve what shall then and there be considered conserning them together with the time and cause of there detention, and that he have then and this said writ
